transcripts.text: In 2016, Ted Cruz blocked a new Supreme Court judge saying the people should get a voice in an election year.
There is a long tradition that you don't do this in an election year.

Now, days before the election, Cruz supports rushing through a new judge, but he's refusing to pass COVID relief to help struggling families and businesses in Texas.  Call Ted Cruz and tell him to pass COVID relief now and let the people's voice be heard on the Supreme Court.  Senator Ted Cruz is letting Texas down.
